title: PP-272 Muzaffargarh: PTI candidate Moazzam Ali Khan defeats PML-N’s Zuhra Bukhari
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jul 17 (APP):Moazzam Ali Khan, a candidate of PTI clinched Punjab Assembly’s PP-272, Muzaffargarh seat by securing 46,069 votes.
According to the results, Syeda Zuhra Bukhari of PML-N got 36,401 votes.
Muhammad Ibrahim of TLP secured 4,360 votes.The turn out remained 51.38 percent.
